Usage: createDensityArea [-help] <box> <density> [-name <obj_name>]

-help                # Prints out the command usage
<box>                # box in <llx> <lly> <urx> <ury> (box, required)
<density>            # Valid values are in increments of 5
                     # (float, required, min=0, max=100)
-name <obj_name>     # name of desity screen (string, optional)